name: Plaintiff not entitled to summary judgment on plaintiff's claim under , as plaintiff failed to establish that plaintiff was actually damaged by defendant's failure to register as a debt collector.  183 F. Supp. 2d 1234.
text: Jurisdiction of courts.  The various district courts of the State shall have concurrent jurisdiction with the circuit courts in all criminal prosecutions for violations of this chapter. [L 1987, c 191, pt of §1]
